  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_safeguarding_concern__snomed_ct_">SAFEGUARDING CONCERN (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_terminology_code">CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY CODE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_safeguarding_concern__snomed_ct_">SAFEGUARDING CONCERN (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct">SNOMED CT</xref>
® concept ID which is used to identify an unresolved issue or concern regarding adult and child safeguarding that requires communication to another 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 or care agency.        </p>
